标记交易月的最后一天¶

In [2]:
def get_LastTradingday(data):
    
    # 每个交易月份所在自然月的月末
    data['monthend'] = data['Trddt'] + MonthEnd(0)
    # 每个交易日距离月末的天数差
    data['date_diff'] = data['monthend'] - data['Trddt']
    # 每个交易月份内的天数差的最小值,赋值df_temp
    date_temp = data.groupby(['Stkcd', 'monthend'])['date_diff'].min()
    # 合并数据 
    date_temp = pd.DataFrame(date_temp)
    date_temp.reset_index(inplace=True)
    date_temp.rename(columns={'date_diff': 'min_diff'}, inplace=True)
    data = pd.merge(data, date_temp, how='left', on=['Stkcd', 'monthend'])
    # 标记最小天数差所在的交易日,即每个交易月份的最后一天
    data['sig'] = np.where(data['date_diff'] == data['min_diff'], 1, np.nan)
    data.drop(columns=['date_diff', 'min_diff', 'monthend'],inplace=True)
    
    return data

动量因子计算¶

In [3]:
def mom(start, end, data):
    
    """
    :param start: Order of starting lag
    :param end: Order of ending lag
    :param df: Dataframe
    :return: Momentum factor
    """
    df = data.copy()
    lag = pd.DataFrame()
    result = 1
    for i in range(start, end):
        lag['mom%s' % i] = df.groupby(['Stkcd'])['Dretwd'].shift(i)
        result = result * (1+lag['mom%s' % i])
    result = result - 1
    
    return result

月度数据导入¶

In [4]:
def loadMainTrdData():
    
    df = pd.read_csv('TRD_Mnth.csv')   
    df = df[df.Markettype.isin([1, 4, 16])]
    df = df[['Stkcd', 'Trdmnt', 'Mretwd', 'Msmvosd']]
    
    # 获取滞后一期的收益率
    # 个股匹配无风险利率（月度），得到超额收益率Ret_Excess, 再滞后一期。
    df_pivot = df.pivot(index='Trdmnt', columns='Stkcd', values='Mretwd')
    df_pivot = df_pivot.shift(-1)
    df_pivot = df_pivot.unstack().reset_index().rename(columns = {0: 'F1_Ret'})
    df = pd.merge(df, df_pivot, on = ['Stkcd', 'Trdmnt'], how='left')
    
    # 导入申万行业数据
    def loadInd():
        
        df = pd.read_excel('最新个股申万行业分类(完整版-截至7月末).xlsx')
        df.columns = ['Exchg', 'Ind_code', 'Stkcd', 'Stknme', 'Industry', 'Ind2', 'Ind3']
        
        df = df[df.Exchg == 'A股']
        df['Stkcd'] = [int(x[:6]) for x in df.Stkcd]
        
        return df[['Stkcd', 'Industry']]
    
    # 合并行业数据
    indInfo = loadInd()
    df = pd.merge(df, indInfo, how='left', on=['Stkcd'])
    
    return df

class Factor_test():
    
    
    def __init__(self, factors, data):
        
        if isinstance(factors,str):
            self.facs = [factors]
        else:
            self.facs = factors
        self.data = data
    

    def data_processing(self):
        
        # 导入股票月度数据
        data_Mn = loadMainTrdData()
        # 全市场等权组合收益率
        Market_eqret = data_Mn.groupby(['Trdmnt']).F1_Ret.mean().reset_index().rename(columns={'F1_Ret':'Market_eqret'})
        
        self.data = get_LastTradingday(self.data)
        self.data.set_index('Trddt',inplace=True)
        # 日度数据提取月末因子值
        data_Dal = self.data[self.data.sig == 1][['Stkcd'] + self.facs]
        data_Dal['Trdmnt'] = [str(i)[:4] + '-' + str(i)[5:7] for i in data_Dal.index]
        data_Dal.reset_index(drop=True,inplace=True)

        # 合并数据 月度收益率及月度市值
        data_Mn = pd.merge(data_Dal, data_Mn, on=['Stkcd','Trdmnt'], how='left')
        data_Mn = data_Mn[data_Mn['Trdmnt'] >= '2010-01']
        
        for factor in self.facs:
            # 因子值数据预处理
            # 中位数去极值
            data_Mn = data_Mn.groupby(['Trdmnt']).apply(extreme_feature_MAD, [factor])
            data_Mn.index = range(len(data_Mn))
            # 标准化 - Zscore
            data_Mn = data_Mn.groupby(['Trdmnt']).apply(get_zscore, [factor])
            data_Mn.index = range(len(data_Mn))
            # 缺失值处理
            data_Mn[factor].fillna(0, inplace=True)
            # 中性化 - 市值行业
            data_Mn['Msmvosd'] = np.log(data_Mn['Msmvosd'])
            data_Mn = data_Mn.groupby(['Trdmnt']).apply(data_scale_neutral_size_ind, 'Msmvosd', 'Industry', [factor])
            data_Mn.index = range(len(data_Mn))
        if len(self.facs) > 1:
            data_Mn['Factor_integrated'] = data_Mn[factor_list].mean(axis=1)

        
        return data_Mn, Market_eqret
    
    
    def get_factor_res(self):
        
        data_Mn,Market_eqret = self.data_processing()
        if len(self.facs) > 1:
            self.facs = 'Factor_integrated'
        else:
            self.facs = self.facs[0]
        tabel = pd.DataFrame(index=[self.facs])
        
        # 因子分组收益率计算
        fac_vw_ret = get_single_sort(data_Mn, self.facs, 'Trdmnt', 10, 'Msmvosd')
        fac_vw_ret = fac_vw_ret.reset_index().pivot(index='Trdmnt', columns='Group', values='Ret').shift(1)
        fac_vw_ret.fillna(0, inplace=True)
        fac_vw_ret['long_short'] = fac_vw_ret['G10'] - fac_vw_ret['G01']
        fac_vw_annret = get_annual_ret(fac_vw_ret,12)
        
        # 因子多空年化波动
        fac_LSvol = get_annual_vol(fac_vw_ret['long_short'], 12)
        # 因子多空最大回撤
        NAV_LS = get_NAV(fac_vw_ret['long_short'], 0)
        fac_maxDrawdownRate = get_maxDrawdownRate(NAV_LS)
        
        fac_ret_G01 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[0])
        fac_ret_G02 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[1])
        fac_ret_G03 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[2])
        fac_ret_G04 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[3])
        fac_ret_G05 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[4])
        fac_ret_G06 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[5])
        fac_ret_G07 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[6])
        fac_ret_G08 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[7])
        fac_ret_G09 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[8])
        fac_ret_G10 = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[9])
        fac_ret_LS = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_vw_annret[10])
        fac_LSvol = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_LSvol)
        fac_maxDrawdownRate = '{:.2%}'.format(fac_maxDrawdownRate)
        
        
        tabel['G01'] = fac_ret_G01
        tabel['G02'] = fac_ret_G02
        tabel['G03'] = fac_ret_G03
        tabel['G04'] = fac_ret_G04
        tabel['G05'] = fac_ret_G05
        tabel['G06'] = fac_ret_G06
        tabel['G07'] = fac_ret_G07
        tabel['G08'] = fac_ret_G08
        tabel['G09'] = fac_ret_G09
        tabel['G10'] = fac_ret_G10
        tabel['多空年化'] = fac_ret_LS 
        tabel['多空年化波动'] = fac_LSvol
        tabel['多空最大回撤'] = fac_maxDrawdownRate

        return tabel

    def group_ret_plot(self, title):
        
        data_Mn,Market_eqret = self.data_processing()
        # 因子分组月均超额收益率计算
        if len(self.facs) > 1:
            self.facs = 'Factor_integrated'
        else:
            self.facs = self.facs[0]   
        fac_vwret = get_single_sort(data_Mn, self.facs, 'Trdmnt', 10, 'Msmvosd')
        fac_vwret = pd.merge(fac_vwret,Market_eqret,on='Trdmnt',how='left')
        fac_vwret['ex_ret'] = fac_vwret['Ret'] - fac_vwret['Market_eqret']
        fac_vwret = fac_vwret.reset_index().pivot(index='Trdmnt', columns='Group', values='ex_ret').shift(1)
        fac_vwret.fillna(0, inplace=True)
        fac_vwret_exret = fac_vwret.mean()
        # 因子分组月均超额绘图
        plt.figure(figsize=(25,12))
        fontsize=15
        plt.rc('font', weight='light', family='SimSun', style='normal', size=str(fontsize))
        X = list(fac_vwret_exret.index)
        y = list(fac_vwret_exret.values)
        plt.bar(X, y, width=0.5)
        plt.yticks([i/1000 for i in range(-8,5)],['{}%'.format(i/10) for i in range(-8,5)])
        plt.title(title)
        plt.show()

    def get_RankIC(self):
        
        data_Mn,Market_eqret = self.data_processing()
        if len(self.facs) > 1:
            self.facs = 'Factor_integrated'
        else:
            self.facs = self.facs[0]
        # IC计算
        RankIC = cal_factor_ic(data_Mn, 'Trdmnt', [self.facs], 'pearson')
        RankIC.rename(columns={self.facs:'RankIC'},inplace=True)
        RankIC['RankIC_temp'] = RankIC['RankIC']
        RankIC.loc[RankIC.index[0], 'RankIC_temp'] = 0
        RankIC['RankIC_cumsum'] = RankIC.RankIC_temp.cumsum()
        
        return RankIC
    
    def RankIC_plot(self,title):
        
        RankIC = self.get_RankIC()
        if len(self.facs) > 1:
            self.facs = 'Factor_integrated'
        else:
            self.facs = self.facs[0]
        # IC绘图
        fig, ax1 = plt.subplots(figsize=(25,12))
        fontsize=15
        plt.rc('font', weight='light', family='SimSun', style='normal', size=str(fontsize))
        plt.rc('axes',unicode_minus='False')
        X = list(RankIC.index)
        y_1 = list(RankIC.RankIC)
        ax1.bar(X, y_1, width=0.4, label=self.facs)
        ax1.set_yticks([i/10 for i in range(-5,4)],['{}%'.format(i * 10) for i in range(-5,4)])
        ax1.set_xticks(X[::10],set_rotation=45)
        ax1.set_title(title)
        plt.setp(ax1.get_xticklabels(),rotation=45)

        ax2 = ax1.twinx()
        y_2 = list(RankIC.RankIC_cumsum)
        ax2.plot(X, y_2, color='black',label="累计RankIC(右轴)")

        fig.legend()
        plt.show()

# 因子计算
def get_RetN_M(df, N, M):
    
    data = df.copy()
    # 剔除交易日未满 N+M 的股票
    freq = data[['Stkcd']].value_counts().reset_index().rename(columns = {0:'freq'})
    data = pd.merge(data, freq, on='Stkcd', how='left')
    data = data[data['freq'] >= N + M]
    data.drop(columns=['freq'],inplace=True)
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)
    
    data['Ret{}_{}'.format(N, M)] = mom(1,N,data)
    data['Ret{}_{}'.format(N, M)] = data.groupby(['Stkcd'])['Ret{}_{}'.format(N, M)].shift(M)
        
    return data

# 因子计算
def get_Ret_RemoveUpLimit_N_M(df, N, M):
    
    data = df.copy()
    # 剥离涨跌停板股票
    data['Clsprc_bef'] = data.groupby(['Stkcd'])['Clsprc'].shift(1)
    data['chg_ratio'] = data['Clsprc'] / data['Clsprc_bef'] - 1 
    
    # data = data[data['chg_ration'] < 0.099]
    data['sig'] = np.where(data['chg_ratio']>=0.099, np.nan, 1)
    data.dropna(subset=['sig'], inplace=True)

    # 剔除交易日未满 N+M 的股票
    freq = data[['Stkcd']].value_counts().reset_index().rename(columns = {0:'freq'})
    data = pd.merge(data, freq, on='Stkcd', how='left')
    data = data[data['freq'] >= N + M]
    data.drop(columns=['freq'],inplace=True)
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)
    
    # 计算动量因子
    data['Ret{}_{}_RemoveUpLimit'.format(N, M)] = mom(1,N,data)
    data['Ret{}_{}_RemoveUpLimit'.format(N, M)] = data.groupby(['Stkcd'])['Ret{}_{}_RemoveUpLimit'.format(N, M)].shift(M)
    data.drop(columns=['Clsprc_bef','chg_ratio','sig'],inplace=True)
    
    return data

# 因子计算
def get_RankMom_N_M(df, N, M):
    
    data = df.copy()
    # 去除ST,ST*股票
    data['sig'] = np.where((data['Trdsta'] == 2) | (data['Trdsta'] == 3), np.nan, 1)
    data.dropna(subset=['sig'],inplace=True)

    # 剔除交易日未满 N+M 的股票
    freq = data[['Stkcd']].value_counts().reset_index().rename(columns = {0:'freq'})
    data = pd.merge(data, freq, on='Stkcd', how='left')
    if N + M >= 125:
        data = data[data['freq'] >= N + M]
    else:
        data = data[data['freq'] >= 125]
        
    data.drop(columns=['freq'],inplace=True)
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)
    
    # 收益率排序 标准化
    data_temp = data[['Stkcd','Trddt','Dretwd']]
    ret_rank = pd.DataFrame(data_temp.groupby(['Trddt'])['Dretwd'].rank(method='first')).rename(columns={'Dretwd':'rank'})
    data_temp = pd.concat([data_temp,ret_rank],axis=1)
    Stk_num = pd.DataFrame(data['Trddt'].value_counts()).reset_index().rename(columns={'index':'Trddt','Trddt':'Stk_num'})
    data_temp = pd.merge(data_temp,Stk_num,on='Trddt',how='left')
    data_temp['RankStd'] = (data_temp['rank'] - ((data_temp['Stk_num'] + 1) * 0.5)) / np.sqrt((data_temp['Stk_num'] - 1) * (data_temp['Stk_num'] + 1) / 12)

    # RankMomN_M 因子信息
    data_temp.set_index('Trddt',inplace=True)
    temp = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd']).RankStd.rolling(N).mean().reset_index().rename(columns={'RankStd':'RankMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)})
    temp['RankMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)] = temp.groupby(['Stkcd'])['RankMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)].shift(M)
    data_temp = pd.merge(data_temp,temp,on=['Trddt','Stkcd'],how='left')
    data_temp = data_temp[['Trddt','Stkcd','RankMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)]]
    # 合并因子
    data = pd.merge(data, data_temp, on=['Trddt','Stkcd'], how='left')
        
    return data

基于位移路程比的平滑动量¶

In [9]:
def get_SmoothMomN_M(df,N,M):
    
    data = df.copy()
    # 剔除交易日未满 N+M 的股票
    freq = data[['Stkcd']].value_counts().reset_index().rename(columns = {0:'freq'})
    data = pd.merge(data, freq, on='Stkcd', how='left')
    data = data[data['freq'] >= N + M]
    data.drop(columns=['freq'],inplace=True)
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)

    # SmoothMomN_M因子
    data_temp = data[['Stkcd','Trddt','Clsprc','Opnprc']]
    data_temp.set_index('Trddt',inplace=True)
    data_temp['chg_ratio'] = data_temp['Clsprc'] / data_temp['Opnprc'] - 1
    data_temp['chg_ratio_abs'] = abs(data_temp['chg_ratio'])
    
    # 滚动计算N日涨跌幅
    lag = pd.DataFrame()
    result = 1
    for i in range(1, N):
        lag['mom%s' % i] = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd'])['chg_ratio'].shift(i)
        result = result * (1+lag['mom%s' % i])
    result = result - 1

    data_temp['chg_ratio_cumsum'] = result
    temp = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd']).chg_ratio_abs.rolling(N).sum().reset_index().rename(columns={'chg_ratio_abs':'chg_ratio_abs_cumsum'})
    data_temp = pd.merge(data_temp,temp,on=['Trddt','Stkcd'],how='left')
    data_temp['SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)] = data_temp['chg_ratio_cumsum'] / data_temp['chg_ratio_abs_cumsum']
    data_temp['SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)] = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd'])['SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)].shift(M)
    # 考虑到因子的单调性 取相反数
    data_temp['SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)] = -data_temp['SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)]
    
    data_temp = data_temp[['Trddt','Stkcd','SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)]]
    # data_temp['SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)] = -data_temp['SmoothMom{}_{}'.format(N, M)]
    # 合并因子

def get_HighN(df,N):
    
    data = df.copy()
    # 剔除交易日未满252的股票
    freq = data[['Stkcd']].value_counts().reset_index().rename(columns = {0:'freq'})
    data = pd.merge(data, freq, on='Stkcd', how='left')
    data = data[data['freq'] >= 252]
    data.drop(columns=['freq'],inplace=True)
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)

    # HighM 因子
    data_temp = data[['Stkcd','Trddt','Clsprc']]
    data_temp.set_index('Trddt',inplace=True)
    temp = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd'])['Clsprc'].rolling(N-1).max().reset_index().rename(columns={'Clsprc':'ClsprcMax_{}'.format(N)})
    temp['ClsprcMax_{}'.format(N)] = temp.groupby(['Stkcd'])['ClsprcMax_{}'.format(N)].shift(1)
    data_temp = pd.merge(data_temp,temp,on=['Trddt','Stkcd'],how='left')
    data_temp['High{}'.format(N)] = data_temp['Clsprc'] / data_temp['ClsprcMax_{}'.format(N)] - 1
    
    data_temp = data_temp[['Trddt','Stkcd','High{}'.format(N)]]
    # 合并因子
    data = pd.merge(data, data_temp, on=['Trddt','Stkcd'], how='left')
    
    return data

# 隔夜动量
def get_OvernightMomN(df,N):
    
    data = df.copy()
    # 剔除交易日未满N的股票
    freq = data[['Stkcd']].value_counts().reset_index().rename(columns = {0:'freq'})
    data = pd.merge(data, freq, on='Stkcd', how='left')
    data = data[data['freq'] >= N]
    data.drop(columns=['freq'],inplace=True)
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)

    # OvernightMomN因子
    data_temp = data[['Stkcd','Trddt','Opnprc','Clsprc']]
    data_temp.set_index('Trddt',inplace=True)
    data_temp['Clsprc_before'] = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd']).Clsprc.shift(1)
    data_temp['Ovnt_chg'] = np.log(data_temp.Opnprc / data_temp.Clsprc_before)
    temp = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd'])['Ovnt_chg'].rolling(N).sum().reset_index().rename(columns={'Ovnt_chg':'OvernightMom{}'.format(N)})
    data_temp = pd.merge(data_temp,temp,on=['Trddt','Stkcd'],how='left')

    # 合并因子
    data_temp = data_temp[['Trddt','Stkcd','OvernightMom{}'.format(N)]]
    data = pd.merge(data, data_temp, on=['Trddt','Stkcd'], how='left')
    
    return data

# 日内反转动量
def get_IntradayMomN(df,N):
    
    data = df.copy()
    # 剔除交易日未满N的股票
    freq = data[['Stkcd']].value_counts().reset_index().rename(columns = {0:'freq'})
    data = pd.merge(data, freq, on='Stkcd', how='left')
    data = data[data['freq'] >= N]
    data.drop(columns=['freq'],inplace=True)
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)

    # 𝐼𝑛𝑡𝑟𝑎𝐷𝑎𝑦𝑀𝑜𝑚20因子
    data_temp = data[['Stkcd','Trddt','Opnprc','Clsprc']]
    data_temp.set_index('Trddt',inplace=True)
    data_temp['Prc_chg'] = np.log(data_temp.Clsprc / data_temp.Opnprc)
    temp = data_temp.groupby(['Stkcd'])['Prc_chg'].rolling(N).sum().reset_index().rename(columns={'Prc_chg':'IntradayMom{}'.format(N)})
    data_temp = pd.merge(data_temp,temp,on=['Trddt','Stkcd'],how='left')

    # 合并因子
    data_temp = data_temp[['Trddt','Stkcd','IntradayMom{}'.format(N)]]
    data = pd.merge(data, data_temp, on=['Trddt','Stkcd'], how='left')

    return data

def get_Rf():
    
    TRD_Nrrate = pd.read_csv(r'TRD_Nrrate.csv',usecols=['Clsdt','Nrrmtdt'])
    # 提取月末无风险利率
    # 每个交易月份所在自然月的月末
    TRD_Nrrate.Clsdt = pd.to_datetime(TRD_Nrrate.Clsdt)
    TRD_Nrrate['monthend'] = TRD_Nrrate['Clsdt'] + MonthEnd(0)
    # 每个交易日距离月末的天数差
    TRD_Nrrate['date_diff'] = TRD_Nrrate['monthend'] - TRD_Nrrate['Clsdt']
    # 每个交易月份内的天数差的最小值,赋值df_temp
    date_temp = TRD_Nrrate.groupby(['monthend'])['date_diff'].min()
    # 合并数据 
    date_temp = pd.DataFrame(date_temp)
    date_temp.reset_index(inplace=True)
    date_temp.rename(columns={'date_diff': 'min_diff'}, inplace=True)
    TRD_Nrrate = pd.merge(TRD_Nrrate, date_temp, how='left', on=['monthend'])
    # 标记最小天数差所在的交易日,即每个交易月份的最后一天
    TRD_Nrrate['sig'] = np.where(TRD_Nrrate['date_diff'] == TRD_Nrrate['min_diff'], 1, np.nan)
    TRD_Nrrate.drop(['date_diff', 'min_diff', 'monthend'],inplace=True,axis=1)
    TRD_Nrrate = TRD_Nrrate[TRD_Nrrate.sig == 1].reset_index(drop=True)

    TRD_Nrrate['Clsdt'] = [x.strftime('%Y-%m') for x in TRD_Nrrate['Clsdt']]

    TRD_Nrrate = TRD_Nrrate[(TRD_Nrrate['Clsdt'] >= '2006-01') & (TRD_Nrrate['Clsdt'] <= '2021-12')]

    # 百分比换成小数
    TRD_Nrrate['Nrrmtdt'] = TRD_Nrrate['Nrrmtdt'] / 100
    TRD_Nrrate.drop(columns=['sig'],inplace=True)
    TRD_Nrrate.rename(columns={'Clsdt':'Trdmnt'},inplace=True)

    return TRD_Nrrate

# 36个月滚动计算残差
def get_res():

    data_Mn = loadMainTrdData()
    TRD_Nrrate = get_Rf()

    ret = data_Mn[data_Mn['Trdmnt'] >= '2006-01'][['Stkcd','Trdmnt','Mretwd']]
    ret.index = range(len(ret))
    ret = pd.merge(ret, TRD_Nrrate, on='Trdmnt', how='left')
    ret = pd.merge(ret, thrfactorMn, on='Trdmnt', how='left')
    ret['exret'] = ret['Mretwd'] - ret['Nrrmtdt']
    ret['month_count'] = ret.groupby(['Stkcd']).cumcount()
    ret['month_num'] = ret.groupby(['Stkcd'])['month_count'].tail(1)
    ret['month_num'] = ret.groupby(['Stkcd'])['month_num'].fillna(method='bfill')
    ret = ret[ret['month_num'] >= 36]
    df_firm = ret[['Stkcd']].drop_duplicates(['Stkcd'])
    df_firm.index = range(len(df_firm))
    df_firm = df_firm.reset_index()
    df_firm = df_firm.rename(columns={'index': 'count'})
    # 存储个股的交易月份总数
    month_num = ret.groupby(['Stkcd'])['month_count'].tail(1)
    month_num = month_num.astype(int)
    month_num = month_num.reset_index(drop=True)
    # 合并数据
    df_firm['month_num'] = month_num

    for Stkcd, count, prog in zip(df_firm['Stkcd'], df_firm['month_num'], range(df_firm['Stkcd'].count()+1)):
        # prog = prog + 1
        # print('processing permno %s' % Stkcd, '/', 'finished', '%.2f%%' % ((prog/df_firm['Stkcd'].count())*100))
        for i in range(count + 1):
            temp = ret[(ret['Stkcd'] == Stkcd) & (i - 35 <= ret['month_count']) & (ret['month_count'] <= i)]
            if temp['Stkcd'].count() < 36:
                pass
            else:
                X = pd.DataFrame()
                # 矩阵求解
                X[['RiskPremium1', 'SMB1', 'HML1']] = temp[['RiskPremium1', 'SMB1', 'HML1']]
                X['intercept'] = 1
                X = X[['intercept', 'RiskPremium1', 'SMB1', 'HML1']]
                X = np.mat(X)
                Y = np.mat(temp[['exret']])
                # Y = np.mat(temp[['Mretwd']])
                # 矩阵求解残差
                rolling_window = temp['Stkcd'].count()
                index = temp.tail(1).index
                res = (np.identity(rolling_window) - X.dot(X.T.dot(X).I).dot(X.T)).dot(Y)
                # 残差存储
                ret.loc[index, 'res'] = res[-1,0]

    return ret

def get_IMFFFactorRegression(df,res):
    
    data = df.copy()
    res['Trddt'] = res['Trdmnt'] + '-01'
    res.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(res.Trddt)
    res.set_index('Trddt',inplace=True)
    # 计算特质动量因子
    temp_sum = res.groupby(['Stkcd'])['res'].rolling(12).sum().reset_index().rename(columns={'res':'res_sum'})
    temp_std = res.groupby(['Stkcd'])['res'].rolling(12).std().reset_index().rename(columns={'res':'res_std'})
    temp_std['res_std']  = temp_std['res_std'] * np.sqrt(12)
    res = pd.merge(res,temp_sum,on=['Stkcd','Trddt'],how='left')
    res = pd.merge(res,temp_std,on=['Stkcd','Trddt'],how='left')
    res['IMFFFactorRegression'] = res['res_sum'] / res['res_std']
    res['IMFFFactorRegression'] = res.groupby(['Stkcd'])['IMFFFactorRegression'].shift(1)
    
    # 数据整合
    res = res[res['Trdmnt'] >= '2010-01']
    res['sig'] = 1 
    res['monthend'] = res['Trddt'] + MonthEnd(0)
    res = res[['IMFFFactorRegression','sig','monthend','Stkcd']]
    
    ## 去除交易时间小于36个月的股票
    data['month_count'] = data.groupby(['Stkcd']).cumcount()
    data['month_num'] = data.groupby(['Stkcd'])['month_count'].tail(1)
    data['month_num'] = data.groupby(['Stkcd'])['month_num'].fillna(method='bfill')
    data = data[data['month_num'] >= 36]
    
    data.Trddt = pd.to_datetime(data.Trddt)
    data = get_LastTradingday(data)
    data['monthend'] = data['Trddt'] + MonthEnd(0)
    data = pd.merge(data, res, on=['sig','monthend','Stkcd'], how='left')
    data.drop(columns=['sig', 'monthend'],axis=1,inplace=True)

    return data

def group_ret_plot(df):
    
        data_Mn = df.copy()
        # 因子分组收益率计算
        fac_vw_ret = get_single_sort(data_Mn, 'Factor_integrated', 'Trdmnt', 10, 'Msmvosd')

        NAV_Short = get_NAV(fac_vw_ret['G01'], 0)
        
        return NAV_LS,NAV_Long,NAV_Short
